OL,3,CWales Decides 2026 - The Debate
OL,5,FWho should run Wales, and what should
OL,6,Ftheir priorities be?
OL,8,FAhead of what promises to be the most
OL,9,Fimportant election in a generation,
OL,10,Fthe leaders of the the six biggest
OL,11,Fpolitical parties in Wales will go
OL,12,Fhead to head in a high-stakes debate
OL,13,Flive from the Senedd.
OL,15,FAt 8pm on Sunday, 19 April, 'Wales
OL,16,FDecides 2026 - The Debate', will put
OL,17,Fthe issues that matter most to voters
OL,18,Ffront and centre.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
