OL,3,CWales Decides 2026 - The Debate
OL,5,FFrom the future of healthcare to the
OL,6,Fongoing cost of living pressures, the
OL,7,Fdebate will tackle the topics shaping
OL,8,Feveryday life across the country.
OL,10,FIf you would like the opportunity to
OL,11,Fput a question directly to those
OL,12,Ftaking part, all you have to do is
OL,13,Femail walesdecides@itv.com.
OL,15,FA selection of your questions will
OL,16,Fthen be put directly to the party
OL,17,Fleaders by ITV Cymru Wales' Political
OL,18,FEditor Adrian Masters who will be
OL,19,Fchairing the debate.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
