OL,3,CWales Decides 2026 - The Debate
OL,5,FSo don't just watch it, be part of
OL,6,F'Wales Decides 2026 - The Debate' live
OL,7,Fon ITV Cymru Wales at 8pm on Sunday,
OL,8,F19 April.
OL,10,FFull Terms and Conditions and Privacy
OL,11,FNotice can be found on the ITV Website.
